      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with everyday practicality. Finished in a timeless metallic coat, the exterior maintains a high gloss, showing only minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seating is plush and free of cracks, while the dashboard and trim remain in excellent shape. All onboard technology, from the responsive touchscreen navigation to the heated seats and premium audio system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history that shows oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent transmission flush. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced just last quarter. This is a dependable, turn-key vehicle for someone who values mechanical integrity and a tidy aesthetic.",
